title: ER S09E19 - Things Change
description:
Episode description from TV.com

Abby treats a psychotic patient who has overdosed on his medication. Eric, Abby&#039;s brother, finally calls. Dr. Gordana Horvat, who attended medical school with Kovac, brings a boy from Croatia who needs heart surgery. Gallant and Pratt receive their match letters. Carter receives bad news about his grandmother. Romano discusses grave options about his arm with Corday.
